data.description: Come see this 4 or 5 br, 2.5 ba home with 2 car garage in one of Ripley's Premiere locations. Vaulted ceiling in living room, large primary suite on the main level with walk in closet. Upstairs balcony overlooking the living room. Three bedrooms on the second level and a large bonus room, or 5th bedroom.  Sun room that leads to large beautiful shaded back yard. New roof 2023 and new central units will be installed at closing.
